###
Regulation
N° 02/2016 OF 24/06/2016 DETERMINING KEY FACTS STATEMENTS AND DISCLOSURE OF ANNUAL PERCENTAGE RATES FOR FIXED TERM CREDIT CONTRACTS BETWEEN A FINANCIAL SERVICE PROVIDER AND A CONSUMER
